## Best Settings for a Cushion Cut Diamond Engagement Ring

### Cushion Solitaire Engagement Ring

The solitaire is the purest cushion cut engagement ring format — stone, prongs, band, nothing else competing for attention. It is also where The Setting Trap is most relevant, because the solitaire gives the stone's character maximum exposure.

**4-prong vs 8-prong:** A 4-prong cushion solitaire places prongs at the four corners of the stone. This leaves the table completely open, shows the full cushion silhouette, and creates the most direct view of the stone's face-up appearance. This is the configuration that best showcases the cushion's soft geometry.

An 8-prong (or double claw) setting adds a second prong at each corner. It increases security — the stone is held at 8 contact points rather than 4 — and reduces the risk of a prong catching on fabric or lifting over time. The cost is a slight reduction in visible stone area. For buyers with active lifestyles or who plan to wear the ring daily without removing it, 8-prong is worth serious consideration.

[![Cushion cut diamond solitaire engagement ring white gold pavé band](https://ion.bluenile.com/sets/Jewelry/Photoshoot/Bluenile/BrioPackshotBox/Rings/501590/501590_M1_CSH_DIM_wht_0100CT_W_Box5_001_1600X1600.jpg)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings?ShapeID=Cushion&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)

Blue Nile's cushion solitaire and pavé solitaire settings start at **[$1,000 for the Petite Solitaire in 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/petite-solitaire-engagement-ring-item-194386?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** (1,020 reviews) and **[$1,180 for the Classic Four Prong Solitaire in Platinum](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/classic-four-prong-solitaire-engagement-ring-item-194156?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** (1,643 reviews). The petite pavé solitaire, which adds melee diamonds to the band, starts at **[$1,255 in 14K Yellow Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/petite-hidden-halo-solitaire-plus-engagement-ring-item-192506?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** (81 reviews). Full guide: [Cushion Solitaire Ring: The Prong Decision That Changes Everything](/cushion-cut-diamond-solitaire-ring).

