### Cushion Halo Engagement Ring

The halo setting is the most popular configuration for cushion cut diamond engagement rings, and for good reason: a square halo perfectly complements the cushion's geometry. The halo's melee diamonds follow the four-sided contour of the cushion's corners, creating a seamless border that amplifies apparent size by 0.3–0.5 carats visually without adding to the center stone cost.

**Square halo vs round halo:** For a cushion center stone, always choose a square (or cushion-shaped) halo rather than a round or oval halo. A round halo around a cushion creates a geometric conflict — the soft, four-sided center fights the circular border. A square halo echoes the cushion's shape and makes the entire ring read as one cohesive design. See [Halo Cushion Cut Diamond Ring: Why This Pairing Works Every Time](/halo-cushion-cut-diamond-ring).

**Double halo:** A double halo adds a second ring of melee diamonds outside the first. This maximizes visual size at the cost of a busier silhouette. It works best on larger center stones (1.5ct+) where the double border doesn't overwhelm the stone.

[![Cushion cut diamond halo engagement ring white gold four-prong](https://ion.bluenile.com/sets/Jewelry/Photoshoot/Bluenile/BrioPackshotBox/Rings/501410/501410_M1_CSH_DIM_wht_0100CT_W_Box5_003_1600X1600.jpg)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings?ShapeID=Cushion&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)

The [Riviera Pavé 14K White Gold at $1,515](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/riviera-pave-engagement-ring-item-195326?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) (390 reviews) is the most-reviewed mid-range pavé solitaire that transitions toward halo territory. For a dedicated halo setting, the [Falling Edge Pavé Halo 14K White Gold at $2,410](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/falling-edge-pave-halo-engagement-ring-item-311113?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) (368 reviews) is Blue Nile's top-reviewed halo choice, with a platinum version at **[$3,010](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/falling-edge-pave-halo-engagement-ring-item-311110?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)**.

