t-rings/design-your-own-ring/petite-micropave-hidden-halo-engagement-ring-item-147511?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">Petite Micropavé Hidden Halo 14K WG</a></td><td>$1,645</td><td>10</td><td>Subtle hidden halo + micropavé</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/falling-edge-pave-halo-engagement-ring-item-311113?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">Falling Edge Pavé Halo 14K WG</a></td><td>$2,410</td><td>368</td><td>Top reviewed halo; best square halo for cushion</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/falling-edge-pave-halo-engagement-ring-item-311110?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">Falling Edge Pavé Halo Platinum</a></td><td>$3,010</td><td>368</td><td>Premium halo; no replating ever</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/milgrain-lace-pave-vintage-engagement-ring-item-315055?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">Milgrain Lace Pavé Vintage 14K WG</a></td><td>$2,650</td><td>17</td><td>Best vintage milgrain setting for cushion</td></tr></tbody></table>

