### Cushion Cut Split Shank Engagement Ring

The split shank setting divides the band into two prongs as it approaches the center stone, creating a visual frame around the base of the cushion. It is a contemporary-leaning style that works particularly well with cushion cut because the gentle split echoes the soft, two-sided geometry of the cushion's corners.

[![Cushion cut diamond split shank engagement ring yellow gold](https://ion.bluenile.com/sets/Jewelry/Photoshoot/Bluenile/BrioSuperImposeBox/Rings/502620/502620_M1_CSH_DIM_wht_0100CT_Y_Box3_004_1600X1600.jpg)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings?ShapeID=Cushion&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)

The [Petite Split Shank Solitaire 14K Yellow Gold at $1,165](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/petite-split-shank-solitaire-engagement-ring-item-192982?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the entry point for split shank styling. The split shank can be worn alone as a statement ring or stacked with a wedding band, though band compatibility varies and should be confirmed before ordering both.

---

### Cushion Cut Three Stone Engagement Ring

A three stone cushion cut engagement ring places the cushion center stone flanked by two smaller side stones. The side stone choice matters significantly for cushion — see [Three Stone Cushion Ring: The Side Stone Nobody Can Find](/three-stone-cushion-cut-diamond-ring) for the full breakdown.

**Best side stone shapes for cushion center:** tapered baguettes (linear, clean contrast), smaller cushions (matched geometry, rare in retail), half-moon stones (curved edge echoes cushion's geometry), and trillion/trilliant cuts (triangular, dramatic).

The three stone cushion configuration is the strongest choice for buyers who want symbolic meaning — the three stones representing past, present, and future — combined with cushion's soft aesthetic. Total ring cost depends heavily on the side stone quality and size, but entry-level three stone cushion builds start around **$3,500–$5,000** total for a 1ct center with quality side stones.

---

### Vintage and Antique Cushion Cut Engagement Rings

The cushion cut's lineage traces to the old mine cut of the 19th century, and the modern cushion modified brilliant inherits that rounded-corner, large-table aesthetic that reads as vintage by association. This makes cushion the single best shape for buyers who want a vintage-influenced engagement ring without purchasing an actual antique.

[![Cushion cut diamond vintage milgrain engagement ring white gold](https://ion.bluenile.com/sets/Jewelry/Photoshoot/Bluenile/BrioPackshotBox/Rings/502482/502482_M1_CSH_DIM_wht_0100CT_W_Box8_003_1600X1600.jpg)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings?ShapeID=Cushion&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)

**Vintage styling choices:**
- **Milgrain borders** — the [Milgrain Lace Pavé Vintage 14K White Gold at $2,650](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/milgrain-lace-pave-vintage-engagement-ring-item-315055?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) (17 reviews) is the standout vintage pick from Blue Nile; tiny bead-like metal detail at the prong edges echoing Edwardian and Victorian metalwork.
- **Filigree** — delicate metal openwork in the gallery (the area below the stone). Creates depth and a lace-like appearance. Classic for Art Nouveau–influenced designs.
- **Rose gold + cushion** — the [Petite Twist Diamond 14K Rose Gold at $1,380](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/petite-twist-diamond-engagement-ring-item-195538?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) (417 reviews) pairs the warmth of rose gold with a twisted pavé band for a vintage-inspired look that flatters the cushion's soft geometry naturally.

For a complete guide to antique and vintage cushion ring styling, see [Antique Cushion Ring: History or Just a Markup?](/antique-cushion-cut-diamond-ring) and [Vintage Cushion Ring: Timeless Style or Overpriced Trend?](/antique-cushion-cut-diamond-ring).

