## Lab-Grown Cushion Cut Diamond Engagement Ring Prices

The lab-grown cushion cut engagement ring market is one of the most competitive in the entire diamond space. At 2ct, the lab option delivers a stone physically and chemically identical to a $13,000 natural for under $3,000. At 3ct, a GIA-certified D-VVS1 lab cushion modified is **$5,962** versus **$32,692** for the closest natural equivalent.

